snippet.title: HuniePop Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Get HuniePop on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/339800/
Or the Official Website: http://www.huniepop.com/

The official release trailer for HuniePop! HuniePop is a dating sim / puzzle game hybrid that launches on January 21st, 2015. It will be available on Steam, Humble and MangaGamer.

HuniePop Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/HuniePop
HuniePop DeviantArt: http://huniepot.deviantart.com/
HuniePop on MangaGamer: http://www.mangagamer.com/detail.php?goods_type=1&product_code=130
Kickstarter Campaign: http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/huniepop/huniepop-a-dating-puzzle-rpg
